arStrings.szText: "The haunting was real. Ghosts wearing Zakarum robes."
in surprise, broken from his foul mood
Oh, perhaps I was wrong to doubt. This is a real threat—as real as the dregs and their affliction. We must act quickly.
There is a Zakarum shrine nearby. Look for signs of hauntings—I want to make sure they have not wandered far. If the Conquerors of Kurast mean to repeat history, we must prepare ourselves.
